00:47:26,260 --> 00:47:28,637
It's all good, Adrian.

632
00:47:28,804 --> 00:47:31,807
Don't you be worrying 
about your old man now.

633
00:47:31,974 --> 00:47:34,977
You got more important things 
to do now.

